{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":507,"text":"My big idea is a very, very small idea"},{"time":4422,"text":"that can unlock billions of big ideas"},{"time":9199,"text":"that are at the moment dormant inside us."},{"time":12589,"text":"And my little idea\nthat will do that is sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16437,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":22237,"text":"This is a room of type A women."},{"time":26769,"text":"This is a room of sleep-deprived women."},{"time":31731,"text":"And I learned the hard way\nthe value of sleep."},{"time":35944,"text":"Two-and-a-half years ago,\nI fainted from exhaustion."},{"time":39078,"text":"I hit my head on my desk."},{"time":40888,"text":"I broke my cheekbone,\nI got five stitches on my right eye."},{"time":45103,"text":"And I began the journey\nof rediscovering the value of sleep."},{"time":50961,"text":"And in the course of that, I studied,"},{"time":53891,"text":"I met with medical doctors, scientists,"},{"time":56493,"text":"and I'm here to tell you"},{"time":58396,"text":"that the way to a more productive,\nmore inspired, more joyful life"},{"time":63956,"text":"is getting enough sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66396,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71612,"text":"And we women are going to lead the way"},{"time":74202,"text":"in this new revolution,\nthis new feminist issue."},{"time":78000,"text":"We are literally going to sleep\nour way to the top -- literally --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":81908,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83393,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88768,"text":"because unfortunately, for men,"},{"time":92103,"text":"sleep deprivation has become\na virility symbol."},{"time":96211,"text":"I was recently having dinner with a guy"},{"time":98425,"text":"who bragged that he had only gotten\nfour hours sleep the night before."},{"time":102922,"text":"And I felt like saying to him --\nbut I didn't say --"},{"time":105519,"text":"I felt like saying, \"You know what?\nif you had gotten five,"},{"time":108670,"text":"this dinner would have been\na lot more interesting.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":111243,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115227,"text":"There is now a kind\nof sleep deprivation one-upmanship."},{"time":119301,"text":"Especially here in Washington,\nif you try to make a breakfast date,"},{"time":122473,"text":"and you say, \"How about eight o'clock?\""},{"time":124370,"text":"they're likely to tell you,\n\"Eight o'clock is too late for me,"},{"time":127357,"text":"but that's OK, I can get\na game of tennis in"},{"time":129446,"text":"and do a few conference calls\nand meet you at eight.\""},{"time":131981,"text":"And they think that means they are\nso incredibly busy and productive,"},{"time":136828,"text":"but the truth is, they're not,"},{"time":139374,"text":"because we, at the moment,"},{"time":141000,"text":"have had brilliant leaders\nin business, in finance, in politics,"},{"time":146885,"text":"making terrible decisions."},{"time":149865,"text":"So a high IQ does not mean\nthat you're a good leader,"},{"time":154251,"text":"because the essence of leadership\nis being able to see the iceberg"},{"time":158499,"text":"before it hits the Titanic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160379,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162146,"text":"And we've had far too many icebergs\nhitting our Titanics."},{"time":166441,"text":"In fact, I have a feeling"},{"time":168667,"text":"that if Lehman Brothers\nwas Lehman Brothers and Sisters,"},{"time":172152,"text":"they might still be around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173637,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":175089,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177190,"text":"While all the brothers were busy\njust being hyper-connected 24/7,"},{"time":182775,"text":"maybe a sister would have\nnoticed the iceberg,"},{"time":185136,"text":"because she would have woken up"},{"time":186699,"text":"from a seven-and-a-half-\nor eight-hour sleep,"},{"time":189699,"text":"and have been able to see the big picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193637,"text":"So as we are facing\nall the multiple crises"},{"time":197839,"text":"in our world at the moment,"},{"time":200268,"text":"what is good for us on a personal level,"},{"time":203109,"text":"what's going to bring more joy,\ngratitude, effectiveness in our lives"},{"time":208670,"text":"and be the best for our own careers,"},{"time":211174,"text":"is also what is best for the world."},{"time":214484,"text":"So I urge you to shut your eyes,"},{"time":219310,"text":"and discover the great ideas\nthat lie inside us;"},{"time":223280,"text":"to shut your engines\nand discover the power of sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226714,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}